1.0.0.name: wordpress/auto-mobile-theme-switcher
1.0.0.description:
Auto Mobile Theme Switcher can change the theme to be displayed according to the detected browser automatically, Make Your Site Mobile/Tablet-Friendly.

For more infomation:

  • http://wpextends.sinaapp.com/plugins/auto-mobile-theme-switcher.html
  • http://wpextends.sinaapp.com

Our Plugins:

  • http://wordpress.org/plugins/auto-pin-it-button/
  • http://wordpress.org/plugins/auto-social-backlink-builder-free/
  • http://wordpress.org/plugins/auto-mobile-theme-switcher/
